<h2>Dear <%= @reserver.title %> <%= @reserver.last_name %>,</h2>
<p>Your reservation number <%= @reservation.reservation_number %> has been updated.</p>
<h2>Reservation Details</h2>
<p>Reservation Number<%= @reservation.reservation_number %></p>
<p>Arriving: <%= @reservation.arrival_date.strftime("%A %d %B %Y") %></p>
<p>Departing: <%= @reservation.departure_date.strftime("%A %d %B %Y")%></p>
<p>Fee: <%= @reservation.fee %></p>
<p>Notes to the Host</p>
<p>Notes: <%= @reservation.notes %></p>
<p>Kind regards,</p>
<p class="signed">Lesley & Mike</p>
